Package: sigvis
Type: Package
Title: Structured Intelligence Governance Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A package for visualizing structured intelligence governance 
    systems. Provides R6 classes for data loading from Google Sheets, 
    graph construction with tidygraph, and network visualization with ggraph.
    Supports template data and client-specific configurations.
